  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria

        Patients must have:

          -  Plasma HIV-1 RNA titers &gt; 10,000 copies/ml.

          -  CD4 cell count &gt; 100 cells/mm3.

        Exclusion Criteria

        Co-existing Condition:

        Patients with any of the following conditions will be excluded:

          -  Any prior anti-retroviral drug therapy.

        Prior Medication:

        Excluded:

        Previous anti-retroviral drug therapy.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
